room_title: Escape room "Santa’s Workshop" by Element of Escape in Sarasota
room_address: 1007 Manatee Ave E Ste. A Bradenton, FL 34208
room_description: I’ve got to let you in on a little secret. We are so glad you are here to help! Jack Frost came into Santa’s Workshop and messed up everything. We elves have been working tirelessly to solve his riddles and get every kid the toy they want but we are stumped! We have one hour until Santa checks in on us and we need to save Christmas! I know you can do it, good luck!
